metadata.name: Fortune! Alpha Caller
metadata.description: Fortune's first Alpha Caller, piramia, has been developing alpha calls since the early 2000's when he began day trading the traditional stock market.  Shortly after, he migrated to blockchain and Bitcoin in 2010.  After creating a venture capital fund in blockchain during 2018 that invested in L1 & L2 protocols, he began day trading crypto and finally moved over to web3 and NFTs in 2021.
